w how natural selection acts at the genetic level and as individuals struggle for survival.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 7aSCIENCE / Life Sciences / Evolution.2bisacsh1 aCraig, Catherine L., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030016315540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300163155423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300163155/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles